# ── 私有内容：真实填充的内容只存本地；_TEMPLATE/ 骨架与目录结构照常上传 ──

# projects/：忽略真实项目，保留 _TEMPLATE
projects/*
!projects/_TEMPLATE/

# reviews/：忽略真实复盘与候选池，保留 _TEMPLATE 与空目录结构
reviews/daily/*
!reviews/daily/.gitkeep
reviews/recurring.md

# style/：忽略真实画像与样本，保留 _TEMPLATE 与空目录结构
style/english-profile.md
style/sharing-profile.md
style/english-samples/*
!style/english-samples/.gitkeep
style/sharing-samples/*
!style/sharing-samples/.gitkeep

# 杂项
*.local.md
.DS_Store
idea.md
